  <notes><![CDATA[
BC-BREAK:
I18Nv2_Locale now has to be instantiated by the factory:
$locale = &I18Nv2_Locale::factory();

CHANGES:
# split I18Nv2_Locale up into several backend modules (LibC, ICU, LDML)
# moved I18Nv2/Locale/* to I18Nv2/Locale/libc/
# integrated I18Nv2/Locale/Windows.php into I18Nv2.php

NEW FEATURES:
+ added I18Nv2_Util, I18Nv2_Util_ICU and I18Nv2_Util_LDML
+ added support to use different backends for the I18Nv2_Locale formatter
. o LibC implementation: as it was using PHPs setlocale(), localeconv() 
. . and the I18Nv2_Locale extensions
. o ICU: International Components for Unicode,
. . see http://www.ibm.com/developerworks/opensource/icu/project/
. o LDML: Locale Data Markup Language,
. . see http://www.OpenI18N.org/modules.php?op=modload&name=Sections&file=index&req=viewarticle&artid=13&page=1

BUGFIXES:
* CS locale libc extension were missing
]]>
  </notes>

